  "remarks": "\nMyan-Oil is, and has been, involved in the repression of the civilian population in Myanmar as it is associated with a person (Asia Sun Trading Company Limited), that has been and is involved in the repression of the civilian population of Myanmar by making available economic resources (aviation fuel) directly or indirectly to or for the benefit of the Myanmar security forces.\n",
